data.description: South Lincoln spacious ranch that is close to many amenities!  This 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home has a roomy and ideal floor plan with a living room that includes a fireplace to cozy up to, an open informal dining and entertainment area with the open kitchen space. There's as deck with a pergola that overlooks a nice sized fenced back yard.  The walkout basement includes a large rec room with bar, large laundry and storage room, a bathroom and a storage room that has potential to be a fourth bedroom. Seller is including a 14mo home warranty with Home Warranty Inc.
